  "prompt": "How widely accepted are credit cards at small businesses and restaurants in Barbados?",
  "response": "Credit cards are generally widely accepted at many small businesses and restaurants in Barbados, especially in tourist areas. Visa and MasterCard are the most commonly accepted cards, while American Express and Discover might be accepted at fewer locations. However, it's always a good idea to have some cash on hand, as some smaller establishments, local street vendors, or businesses in more rural areas may not accept credit cards. Additionally, it's wise to inform your bank of your travel plans, so they don't flag your transactions as suspicious and freeze your card.",
